extendedInfo.description: Darkpsyckedelic.com is a free online radio that streams psychedelic music. With this application you will be able to listen to the radio everywhere!It has has a simple and intuitive interface, works fast and smooth and has NO adds!The current channels available are:*Dark Psychedelic : darkpsy, hightech, psycore, and more. Higher tempo for a non-stop night*Dark Forest : dig into a deep dark forest, and feel the organic psychedelia in your mind*Dark Ambient : solitude, melancholy, confinement, and isolation in a dark remote placeThe application is currently available in English, French, Spanish and Russian (automatically detected and configured).Your comments are always welcome!
